<%#
  Markdown variant of the tier badge. Pass `collective:` as a local.
  Mirrors the HTML partial: emits nothing for main collectives, archived
  collectives, or tenants where stripe_billing is off.
%>
<% unless collective.is_main_collective? || collective.archived? || !T.must(collective.tenant).feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
<% if collective.paid_tier? %>
**Plan:** Paid ($3/mo)<%= collective.billing_exempt? ? " (exempt)" : "" %>
<% elsif collective.requires_stripe_billing? %>
**Plan:** Billing lapsed — paid features paused
<% else %>
**Plan:** Free
<% end %>
<% end %>
